  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enjoy the thrill of walking the fine line between hiding and getting caught!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Reach for the ultimate high score!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >[Time Attack]</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Compete for the fastest clear time and earn a top spot on the leaderboards!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Pay attention to the patrolling characters and carefully decide when to play and when to hide!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >[Battle]</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Compete against friends or CPU controlled opponents for the highest score!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Be bold and take risks to rack up the most points and win the game!</p>",
